default(ICE
default is a UK-based international organisation with 
defaultover
default 80,000 members ranging from students to professional civil engineers. It is an educational and qualifying body and has charitable status under UK law. Founded in 1818, ICE has become recognised worldwide for its excellence as a centre of learning, as a qu
defaultalifying body and as a public voice for the profession.
